chorus:chorus-domain chorus:builtBy chorus:chorusStream .
chorus:convergence-domain chorus:builtBy chorus:chorusStream .

# Gathering domains → gatheringStream
chorus:music-domain chorus:builtBy chorus:gatheringStream .
